#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-followupreminderagent; is an akonadi agent which follow up reminder "
"mail"
msgstr "&i18n-followupreminderagent; je posrednik akonadi, ki sledi opomnikom"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &i18n-followupreminderagent;"
msgstr "Uporaba &i18n-followupreminderagent;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <menuchoice><guimenu>Options</guimenu><guimenuitem>Create Follow Up "
"Reminder</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in &kmail;'s composer window to open a "
"dialog which allows you to create a reminder to follow up your current email "
"at a specific date."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ustvari "
"opomnik za nadaljevanje</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v oknu za ustvarjanje "
"&kmail;, da odprete pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko ustvarite opomnik za "
"spremljanje vašega trenutnega po e-pošti na določen datum."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&i18n-followupreminderagent; Dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&i18n-followupreminderagent; Pogovorno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&i18n-followupreminderagent; Dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&i18n-followupreminderagent; Pogovorno okno</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>&i18n-followupreminderagent; Dialog</para>"
msgstr "<para>&i18n-followupreminderagent; Pogovorno okno</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the arrow-down button against the <guilabel>Date</guilabel> field to "
"select the date from the &kde; calendar widget. It is also possible to "
"choose your calendar for the reminder using the <guilabel>Store ToDo in</"
"guilabel> drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite puščico navzdol proti polju <guilabel>Datum</guilabel>, da "
"izberete datum iz &kde; pripomočka za koledar. Svoj koledar za opomnik lahko "
"izberete tudi s spustnim seznamom <guilabel>Shrani opravila v</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove reminders you have scheduled, use <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kmail;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> then "
"select the <guilabel>Plugins</guilabel> page in &kmail; and press the "
"configuration button against the <guilabel>Followup Reminder Agent</"
"guilabel> item. Then use the context menu launched with a &RMB; click on a "
"reminder item to select the <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem> action."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti opomnike, ki ste jih načrtovali, uporabite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kmail;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> nato izberite stran "
"<guilabel>Vtičniki</guilabel> v &kmail;-u in pritisnite gumb za "
"konfiguracijo proti elementu <guilabel>Agent za nadaljnje opomnike</"
"guilabel>. Nato uporabite kontekstni meni, ki ga zaženete z &RMB; kliknite "
"element opomnika, da izberete dejanje <guimenuitem>Izbriši</guimenuitem>."

